This was a fun simple program i wrote to do tip calculations for larger groups. Its easy enough to use the calc app on a phone, but i wanted to create a app to use on
a mobile phone for large groups and to be able to adjust the percentage quickly. It has also come in handy for situations where restuatants automatically add gratuity
to the bill. There have been situations where the restaurant percentages were a bit inflated compared to the percentage.


